{
  "texts": [
    "The model understands the background, which is related to careful rapid engineering, not just aligning keywords.",
    "Linguistically Grounded Suggestion SystemsNext-generation conversational recommendation systems find their cognitive basis in large language models.",
    "Think of it as a proactive shopping assistant that probes \"Are you seeking something casual or more formal?\"",
    "Alternatively \"Do you have a set budget?\"",
    "These engines not only provide products but also learn and improve their Recommendations in actual time using well-organized cues."
  ]
}